Description (EN): winding coil pitch or coil span expressed in slots (coil_pitch1=Zs/(2p)->full-pitch distributed winding, coil_pitch1<Zs/(2p)->chorded/shorted-pitch distributed winding, coil_pitch1=1->tooth-winding). Coil pitch is sometimes written 1/9 means Input.Magnetics.coil_pitch1=9-1=8
Class description: single layer overlapping integral distributed winding
